      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 7225.35,
      "end": 7225.95,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 7231.05,
      "end": 7233.45,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "朋友东西会你你会卖那个吗？对不起，我真的不会卖。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 7234.25,
      "end": 7235.15,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我不知道咋卖。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 7237.15,
      "end": 7238.25,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以这就体现了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 7240.05,
      "end": 7242.25,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "其实顿顿比我懂的更多呀。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 7245.05,
      "end": 7246.05,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "知识盲区。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 7247.05,
      "end": 7293.05,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我们之前有一段时间，我跟他说过，之前有一段时间我们直播间真的，那段时间太惨了，太难了。挣扎一天卖不了多少钱。直播间动动人数从，有一段时间上上千，现在上三千了，感觉哎呀，是不是苦日子要到头了，结果又掉掉破一千了。剩七八百人了。就窘迫到自己不知道咋办了，还在复盘，复盘的时候生怕自己不够坦诚批评，找不到原因，互相辱骂羞辱那种。对彼此非常狠。你们没有是吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 7293.05,
      "end": 7293.55,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "奇怪。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 7293.55,
      "end": 7293.95,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 7316.05,
      "end": 7316.65,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "我们没有。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 7317.05,
      "end": 7318.05,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "怎么可能没有？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 7318.35,
      "end": 7319.05,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "怎么可能没有？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 24,
      "start": 7319.35,
      "end": 7319.65,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 25,
      "start": 7320.25,
      "end": 7321.05,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "听懂了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 6
    },
    {
      "idx": 26,
      "start": 7322.05,
      "end": 7324.05,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但是还是没用，反正人数就是少。",
